<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>GymPal — Roadmap</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --green: #4CAF7D;
    --green-dim: #1a3a28;
    --green-border: #2d5a3d;
    --green-text: #3a9e6e;
    --bg: #0e0e0e;
    --bg-2: #151515;
    --bg-3: #1a1a1a;
    --bg-4: #1f1f1f;
    --border: #232323;
    --border-2: #2a2a2a;
    --text-primary: #f0f0f0;
    --text-secondary: #888;
    --text-muted: #444;
    --amber: #EF9F27;
    --amber-dim: #2a1f0a;
    --amber-border: #4a3510;
    --blue: #6699dd;
    --blue-dim: #1a1f2a;
    --blue-border: #2a3550;
    --purple: #9f8fef;
    --purple-dim: #1e1a30;
    --purple-border: #332a50;
    --font: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text-primary); font-family: var(--font); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
  a { color: var(--green); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .container { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

  nav { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: rgba(14,14,14,0.92); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
  .nav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 24px; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .nav-logo-icon { width: 30px; height: 30px; background: var(--green); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .nav-logo-icon svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
  .nav-logo-name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
  .nav-badge { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--green); background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); border-radius: 5px; padding: 2px 7px; }
  .nav-feedback { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--green); background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 14px; transition: background .15s; text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-feedback:hover { background: #1e3f2e; text-decoration: none; }

  .hero { padding: 72px 0 56px; }
  .hero-eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-text); background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); border-radius: 20px; padding: 4px 12px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .hero-eyebrow-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--green); border-radius: 50%; animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.4} }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(30px, 6vw, 46px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero h1 span { color: var(--green); }
  .hero-desc { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .hero-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .meta-item { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .meta-item strong { color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 600; }
  .meta-dot { width: 3px; height: 3px; background: var(--text-muted); border-radius: 50%; }

  .version-strip { background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 64px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .version-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .version-number { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .version-number span { color: var(--green); }
  .version-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; max-width: 380px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .version-next-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--amber); background: var(--amber-dim); border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 5px 12px; }
  .version-next-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 6px; max-width: 220px; line-height: 1.5; }

  .section { margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .section-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.9px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .label-green { color: var(--green-text); }
  .label-blue  { color: var(--blue); }
  .label-amber { color: var(--amber); }
  .label-purple{ color: var(--purple); }
  .section-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.3px; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .section-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 3px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .features { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .feature { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; transition: border-color .15s, background .15s; }
  .feature:hover { border-color: var(--border-2); background: var(--bg-3); }
  .feature-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 9px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .icon-green  { background: var(--green-dim); }
  .icon-blue   { background: var(--blue-dim); }
  .icon-amber  { background: var(--amber-dim); }
  .icon-purple { background: var(--purple-dim); }
  .icon-green  svg { stroke: var(--green); }
  .icon-blue   svg { stroke: var(--blue); }
  .icon-amber  svg { stroke: var(--amber); }
  .icon-purple svg { stroke: var(--purple); }
  .feature-icon svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }
  .feature-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .feature-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .feature-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; }
  .feature-right { flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 1px; }
  .tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; border-radius: 5px; padding: 2px 8px; white-space: nowrap; border: 1px solid; }
  .tag-wip     { color: var(--green);  background: var(--green-dim);  border-color: var(--green-border); }
  .tag-planned { color: var(--text-muted); background: var(--bg-4); border-color: var(--border); }
  .tag-eval    { color: var(--amber);  background: var(--amber-dim);  border-color: var(--amber-border); }
  .tag-premium { color: var(--amber);  background: var(--amber-dim);  border-color: var(--amber-border); }
  .tag-future  { color: var(--purple); background: var(--purple-dim); border-color: var(--purple-border); }

  .cta-section { background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px 32px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .cta-section h2 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.3px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .cta-section p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto 28px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary { font-family: var(--font); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background: var(--green); color: #0a2016; border: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 11px 22px; cursor: pointer; transition: background .15s; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #5cc48c; text-decoration: none; color: #0a2016; }
  .btn-secondary { font-family: var(--font); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background: transparent; color: var(--text-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 11px 22px; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color .15s, color .15s; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: #444; color: var(--text-primary); text-decoration: none; }

  footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 28px 0; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .hero { padding: 48px 0 40px; }
    .nav-inner { padding: 12px 16px; }
    .container { padding: 0 16px; }
    .cta-section { padding: 28px 20px; }
    .version-strip { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <div class="nav-logo">
      <div class="nav-logo-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0a2016" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8zM6 1v3M10 1v3M14 1v3"/></svg>
      </div>
      <span class="nav-logo-name">GymPal</span>
      <span class="nav-badge">Beta</span>
    </div>
    <a class="nav-feedback" href="mailto:cordellasandrodev9@proton.me?subject=GymPal%20Feedback">Scrivi feedback</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="container">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow-dot"></div>
      Sviluppo attivo
    </div>
    <h1>Cosa stiamo<br>costruendo <span>su GymPal.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      Una panoramica trasparente di ciò su cui stiamo lavorando, cosa è in arrivo e dove vogliamo portare il prodotto. Le priorità si adattano continuamente in base ai feedback degli utenti.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="meta-item">Versione corrente: <strong>0.7.7</strong></div>
      <div class="meta-dot"></div>
      <div class="meta-item">Piattaforma: <strong>Android</strong></div>
      <div class="meta-dot"></div>
      <div class="meta-item">Aggiornata: <strong>Aprile 2026</strong></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="version-strip">
    <div>
      <div class="version-label">Ciclo attuale</div>
      <div class="version-number"><span>0.7</span>.x</div>
      <div class="version-desc">Focus su miglioramenti UX, rifinitura dell'interfaccia e correzione dei bug emersi durante i test interni. Nessuna funzionalità major in questo ciclo.</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="version-label">Prossimo traguardo</div>
      <div class="version-next-tag">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        0.8 — early testers
      </div>
      <div class="version-next-sub">Prima versione aperta a tester esterni. Stiamo preparando l'app per questo passaggio.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- IN LAVORAZIONE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label label-green">In lavorazione</div>
    <div class="section-title">Attualmente in sviluppo</div>
    <div class="section-desc">Le aree su cui stiamo lavorando in questo momento, nel ciclo 0.7.x e nella transizione verso 0.8.</div>
    <div class="features">

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><path d="M9 9h6M9 12h6M9 15h4"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Visualizzazione scheda durante l'allenamento</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Consulta la scheda in corso, naviga tra gli esercizi con swipe e accedi ai dettagli di ogni serie senza interrompere il flusso.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-wip">In corso</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Swipe tra schede ed esercizi</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Navigazione gestuale per scorrere tra schede e tra gli esercizi di una scheda, senza dover usare i bottoni.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-wip">In corso</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Rifinitura dell'interfaccia</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Revisione continua di spaziature, tipografia, transizioni e coerenza visiva su tutte le schermate.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-wip">Continuo</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"/><path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 102.13-9.36L1 10"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Pull-to-refresh su liste e grafici</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Swipe verso il basso per ricaricare manualmente i dati su qualsiasi lista o pagina grafica dell'app.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-wip">In corso</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Ricerca esercizi migliorata</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Scroll automatico al nuovo esercizio appena creato, filtri rivisti e un'esperienza di ricerca più coerente in tutta l'app.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-wip">In corso</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Allenamento a cavallo della mezzanotte</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Gestione corretta del caso in cui una sessione inizia prima e termina dopo mezzanotte — il giorno viene assegnato in modo coerente.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-wip">In corso</span></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROSSIMAMENTE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label label-blue">Prossimamente</div>
    <div class="section-title">In arrivo</div>
    <div class="section-desc">Funzionalità confermate per i prossimi aggiornamenti. L'ordine di sviluppo viene definito in base ai feedback e alle priorità emergenti — non è fisso.</div>
    <div class="features">

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Streak di allenamento</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Giorni consecutivi tracciati automaticamente, con streak corrente e record personale. Un promemoria quotidiano della propria costanza.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 6h13M8 12h13M8 18h13M3 6h.01M3 12h.01M3 18h.01"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Record personali</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Peso massimo per ogni esercizio, sessione più lunga e record di giorni consecutivi — aggiornati automaticamente ad ogni allenamento.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Calendario nel notebook con note</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Vista mensile nella sezione notebook. Tap su un giorno per aggiungere note libere, tag o collegare la sessione registrata.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Allenamento libero</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Avvia una sessione senza scheda e aggiungi esercizi al momento. Utile anche per chi vuole deviare dal programma senza rinunciare al tracciamento.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Pagina progressi ampliata</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Nuovi tipi di grafico (volume totale, ripetizioni, frequenza), confronto tra periodi e una visione più ricca dell'andamento nel tempo.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 9.81a19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 012 .92h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 8.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Cronometro in barra notifiche e lock screen</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Il timer del recupero rimane visibile anche con il telefono bloccato o mentre si usa un'altra app. Nessun bisogno di riaprire GymPal.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Immagini e video sugli esercizi</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Scheda esercizio con indicazioni visive sull'esecuzione corretta, per ridurre il rischio di errori tecnici — soprattutto per chi si allena da solo.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <div class="feature-title">Creazione rapida scheda — editing massivo</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Costruisci o modifica un'intera scheda in pochi passaggi senza aprire ogni esercizio singolarmente. Ideale per chi costruisce spesso nuovi programmi.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-right"><span class="tag tag-planned">Pianificato</span></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IN VALUTAZIONE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label label-amber">In valutazione</div>
    <div class="section-title">Idee confermate, tempi da definire</div>
    <div class="section-desc">Feature che vogliamo realizzare, ma che richiedono più progettazione o dipendono dall'evoluzione del prodotto.</div>
    <div class="features">

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-amber"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg></div>
